snippet.title: *FULL* Submerged Map Tasks Overview | Among Us
snippet.description:
Hey everyone, this video covers all the tasks on the Submerged custom Among Us map! I’ve tried to cover off as much as I can in this video while not making it too long.

Remember to show some love to all the people involved with Submerged: https://5ubmerged.carrd.co/

Edit: Lot of people in the comments keep asking - the map is already out! It is available on PC included with a variety of popular modpacks such as Town of Us and The Other Roles. It is also available as a standalone mod: https://github.com/SubmergedAmongUs/Submerged
This map is a community made project. It is not created by the developers of Among Us and is not part of the official game. It is only available on PC via modding.


Follow Arctic Zephyr!
Twitter: https://twitter.com/arctic_zeph

#Zeph #amongus #among #us #5upmerged

0:00 Introduction
0:34 SUBMERGED
1:03 PURCHASE BREAKFAST
1:37 MICROWAVE LUNCH
2:10 RESET BREAKERS
2:27 CLEAR URCHINS
2:53 CYCLE REACTOR
3:14 UNLOCK MANIFOLDS
3:26 RECONNECT PIPING
3:52 DISPENSE WATER
4:07 RESHELVE BOOKS
4:40 OXYGENATE SEA PLANTS
5:08 SUBMIT SCAN
5:31 STEADY HEARTBEAT
6:09 FEED PET FISH
6:29 ALIGN TELESCOPE
6:52 SPOT WHALE SHARK
7:10 LOCATE VOLCANIC ACTIVITY
7:27 SHOOT DEPTH CHARGES
7:53 SORT SCUBA GEAR
8:16 CLEAN GLASS
8:29 IDENTIFY SPECIMEN

10:10 MOP PUDDLES
11:03 PLUG LEAKS
11:32 BALLAST SABOTAGE
12:24 FIX COMMS
12:40 OXYGEN SABOTAGE
